Ask HN: Possible to have HnRSS.org link to discussion instead of post link?
text:
It seems HnRSS only lets you have the url of its results link to the post's link. This will link to the discussion for self posts like Ask HN or Show HN, but will link to the url for a regular post.

Any way to have it link to the discussion? It's often more interesting than the link itself.
